data.description: Huge Price reduction !!! Well maintained house located in highly desirable & attractive Alhambra neighborhood.Super convenient location to business and retail shops,supermarkets,schools,restaurants,transportation,park.golf course near by,short distance to DTLA.Subject property features 4 Bedrooms,2.5 Bath with almost 1,900 Sq/Ft.cozy fire place.The formal dining room next to breakfast nook.First time on the market for almost 50 years.Very good ADU potential in the future.Well maintained kitchen with plenty of cabinets.Large master bedroom and family room and separate living room area.Long drive way and very well maintained in & out.Very open floor plan & See it to believe it !!!!
